---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageSection from "../components/PageSection.astro";
import ContentSection from "../components/ContentSection.astro";
---
<Layout
        title="Photography | Techit Thawiang"
        description="Collection of my photography stuff."
        navTitle="Photography<br/>captures life’s vivid harmony."
        ogTitle="Actually I do photographing too."
        ogDescription="Collection of my photography stuff."
        ogUrl="https://techit.win/photography"
>
    <PageSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <h1>One, two, shoot! 📸</h1>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p style="font-size:13px;">Warning: Massive image sizes.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >I started <span class="text-highlight">photographing</span> things when I was just 9 years old, thanks to my first smartphone. It was super cheap and not the best in quality, but it held a special place in my heart because my mum bought it for me.</p>
            <p >In 2023, I had the amazing opportunity to play with one of my friend's DSLR cameras. That day, I learned how to use a DSLR, and the difference in quality was astonishing compared to my early smartphone photos! It was a fun and eye-opening experience that reignited my passion for photography, making me excited to capture the world with better tools.</p>
        </ContentSection>
        <ContentSection>
            <p >Here's some of them.</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 photography-grid">
                <a class="cell" href="https://j1.techit.win/images/photography/IMG_4183.JPG">
                    <img loading="lazy" alt="IMG_4183.JPG" src="https://j1.techit.win/images/photography/IMG_4183.JPG"/>
